name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy listing from Aliexpress to Shopee

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You can copy the listing from Aliexpress with two buttons and paste it into Shopee.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
On the Aliexpress website - click the "Copy listing" button.
On the Shopee website, click the "Insert Listing" button.
Listing copied!

Extensions copies:
 - Name
 - Description
 - Pictures
 - Stock

All sites - Aliexpress
All sites - Shopee
